OL,3,C'We fell short': Fire chief admits
OL,4,Cfailings after flood victim found by
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FA fire brigade has admitted it "fell
OL,8,Fshort" after the body of an 83-year-
OL,9,Fold woman was found in floodwater by
OL,10,Fher son following aborted attempts to
OL,11,Frescue her.
OL,13,FPaul Gilbert discovered his mother,
OL,14,FMaureen, floating in the water at her
OL,15,Fhome in Tapton Terrace, Chesterfield,
OL,16,FDerbyshire, on 21 October 2023.
OL,18,FMrs Gilbert had become trapped when
OL,19,Fthe River Rother burst its banks and
OL,20,Fflooded her house during Storm Babet.
