OL,3,C'We fell short': Fire chief admits
OL,4,Cfailings after flood victim found by
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FChesterfield Coroner's Court was told
OL,8,Ffirefighters did everything they could
OL,9,Fto rescue Mrs Gilbert at her terraced
OL,10,Fproperty on the evening of 20 October,
OL,11,Fbut were unable to reach her.
OL,13,FCrews failed to return to the property
OL,14,Fafter a request to go back was
OL,15,F"mislogged" while Derbyshire Fire and
OL,16,FRescue Service's control room systems
OL,17,Fwere down.
