OL,7,FMrs Gilbert was one of at least seven
OL,8,Fpeople who died as a result of Storm
OL,9,FBabet, which caused disruption across
OL,10,Fthe UK.
OL,12,FNeil Porteous, an incident commander
OL,13,Ffor the fire service, said he
OL,14,Frequested that Tapton Terrace be
OL,15,Freinspected the following day but this
OL,16,F"was not communicated", the inquest
OL,17,Fheard.
