OL,3,C'We fell short': Fire chief admits
OL,4,Cfailings after flood victim found by
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FClive Stanbrook, an area manager for
OL,8,Fthe service, told the inquest on
OL,9,FTuesday: "This had clearly not been
OL,10,Fhanded over to the next shift the next
OL,11,Fday. We should have gone back in the
OL,12,Fmorning. We fell short."
OL,14,FParts of the control room system had
OL,15,F"completely failed" when the request
OL,16,Fto check on Mrs Gilbert was made, the
OL,17,Finquest heard.
