OL,3,C'We fell short': Fire chief admits
OL,4,Cfailings after flood victim found by
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FThe coroner was told wheelie bins and
OL,8,Ffence panels were floating in the
OL,9,Fwater when firefighters attempted to
OL,10,Fmake contact with Mrs Gilbert the
OL,11,Fevening before.
OL,13,FMr Porteous said: "It was massive
OL,14,Famounts of water. The front gardens
OL,15,Fwere completely underwater. It was a
OL,16,Fdifficult scene to look at.
OL,18,F"Numerous wheelie bins just floating
OL,19,Fon top of the water. Loads of debris
OL,20,Ffloating. Manhole covers had lifted as
OL,21,Fwell."
