OL,3,C'We fell short': Fire chief admits
OL,4,Cfailings after flood victim found by
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FMr Porteous said the crew knew Mrs
OL,8,FGilbert was inside the property
OL,9,Fbecause her son had spoken to her on
OL,10,Fthe phone but then lost contact.
OL,12,FHe said: "It was just a very, very
OL,13,Fdifficult scene. We had done
OL,14,Feverything we could possibly do.
OL,16,F"We don't like to leave people behind.
OL,17,FIt was just too dangerous ` it was
OL,18,Fgetting too dark.
OL,26,@tD@JOUxD@AOU
