OL,3,C'We fell short': Fire chief admits
OL,4,Cfailings after flood victim found by
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,F"The crew said 'Can we go in?' and at
OL,8,Fthat point I had to stop them and
OL,9,Fexplain why, and they understood."
OL,11,FAt 7.22pm, the rescue crew left the
OL,12,Fscene at Tapton Terrace and Mr
OL,13,FPorteous made the request for a
OL,14,Freinspection the next day.
OL,16,FMr Gilbert said it was "disappointing"
OL,17,Fthat he discovered his mother himself.
OL,19,FThe inquest will continue on Wednesday
OL,20,Fmorning.
